#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks home page"
msgstr "Domaća stranica s obeleživačima"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module lets you configure the bookmarks home page."
msgstr "U ovom modulu možete podesiti domaću stranicu obeleživača."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the bookmarks home page enter <userinput>bookmarks:/</userinput> in "
"the location bar."
msgstr ""
"Domaću stranicu obeleživača možete prikazati unošenjem <userinput>bookmarks:/"
"</userinput> u traku lokacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings in this module are also accessible by entering "
"<userinput>bookmarks:/config</userinput> in the location bar."
msgstr ""
"Postavkama u ovom modulu može se pristupiti i unošenjem "
"<userinput>bookmarks:/config</userinput> u traku lokacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "General settings"
msgstr "Opšte postavke"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of columns to show"
msgstr "Broj kolona:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Folders are automatically distributed in several columns. The optimal number "
"of columns depends on the width of the &konqueror; window and the number of "
"bookmarks you have."
msgstr ""
"Fascikle se automatski raspoređuju u nekoliko kolona. Optimalan broj kolona "
"zavisi od širine <application>K‑osvajačevog</application> prozora i broja "
"obeleživača."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show folder backgrounds"
msgstr "Pozadine fascikli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable it on slow system to disable background images."
msgstr "Ispraznite na sporom sistemu kako biste isključili slike pozadine."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show bookmarks without folder"
msgstr "Obeleživači bez fascikle"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is unchecked, bookmarks at the root of the hierarchy (not "
#| "in a folder) are not displayed. If checked, they are gathered in a \"root"
#| "\" folder."
msgid ""
"If this option is unchecked, bookmarks at the root of the hierarchy (not in "
"a folder) are not displayed. If checked, they are gathered in a “root” "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"Ako je prazno, ne prikazuju se obeleživači u korenu hijerarhije (van "
"fascikli). Ako je popunjeno, sabrani su u „korenoj“ fascikli."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flatten bookmarks tree"
msgstr "Spljošteno stablo obeleživača"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sub-folders are shown within their parent by default. If you activate this "
"option, sub-folders are displayed on their own. It looks less nice but it "
"may help if you have a very big folder you want to spread in two columns."
msgstr ""
"Potfascikle se podrazumevano prikazuju unutar roditeljske fascikle. Ako "
"aktivirate ovu opciju, potfascikle će se prikazivati samostalno. Ne izgleda "
"tako lepo, ali može biti od pomoći ako imate veoma veliku fasciklu koju "
"želite da razdvojite u dve kolone."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show system places"
msgstr "Sistemska mesta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Show a box with common places (Home, Network, ...). Useful if you use "
#| "&konqueror; as a file manager."
msgid ""
"Show a box with common places (Home, Network, …). Useful if you use "
"&konqueror; as a file manager."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz okvira sa uobičajenim mestima (domaće, mreža, ...) Korisno ako vam je "
"<application>K‑osvajač</application> menadžer fajlova."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pixmap cache"
msgstr "Keš bitmapa"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disk cache size"
msgstr "Veličina keša na disku:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify how much disk space is used to cache the pixmaps."
msgstr "Zadajte koliko se prostora na disku koristi za keširanje bitmapa."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear Cache"
msgstr "Očisti keš"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Remove all cached images. This may be necessary if some favicons become "
#| "corrupt and don't refresh automatically."
msgid ""
"Remove all cached images. This may be necessary if some favicons become "
"corrupt and don’t refresh automatically."
msgstr ""
"Uklanja sve keširane slike. Ovo može biti potrebno ako su neke favikonice "
"oštećene i ne osvežavaju se automatski."
